From 7ec67008007e53ef9e05e7b0375fbb236585d35a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: jeeminso <jeeminso@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 18 Feb 2025 17:22:13 +0900
Subject: [PATCH] Fix for unremoved empty partitions when DELETE condition
 contained nondeterministic functions

such as `now()`. This is a regression introduced by #15924 which
incorrectly prevented normalizing nondeterministic functions during
WhereClauseAnalyzer.resolvePartitions().

The scope of #15924 was 'Do not normalize nondeterministic functions
during analysis' but WhereClauseAnalyzer.resolvePartitions() is not
part of the analysis phase.
